    "This study highlights the potential for AI to improve aid in the early stages of research and make the process more efficient.",
    "However, it is important to note that Macdonald and colleagues found that ChatGPT made coding mistakes, and provided references that did not exists (though they did not provide an accounting of how frequent these errors were).",
